    <item>
      <title>中国对欧盟进口猪肉启动反倾销调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/china-launches-anti-dumping-probe-on-imports-of-eu-pork</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国对从欧盟进口的猪肉发起反倾销调查，这是一项针对性较强的措施，也是北京和布鲁塞尔之间贸易紧张局势的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/china-launches-anti-dumping-probe-on-imports-of-eu-pork</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 07:28:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
